    "created_at": "2015-08-13T04:36:34Z",
    "updated_at": "2015-08-13T04:36:34Z",
    "body": "If you execute Electron with no command line params it will look for the following:\n\n```\nresources/app.asar\nresources/app\nresources/default_app\n```\n\nYou can however execute Electron from command line and pass in your app as a param:\n\n```\nelectron your_app\n```\n"
