    "created_at": "2015-08-13T14:48:46Z",
    "updated_at": "2015-08-13T14:48:46Z",
    "body": "If your app is in the resources folder either as an app.asar, contained in a folder called app or default_app you won't need to tell Electron where it is. The folder resources\\app or resources\\default_app must be the root of your application. \n\nHaving your app in the app folder like this is most likely not going to work:\n\n```\nresources\\app\\my_app\n```\n\nThe way I choose to run Electron is to just put my app in resources\\app and double click Electron.exe.\n"
